I"W<p><b>Ingredients</b></p>
<ul>
  <li>1 teaspoon ground turmeric</li>
  <li>½ teaspoon cumin</li>
  <li>½ teaspoon cinnamon</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon salt</li>
  <li>½ teaspoon black pepper (ground)</li>
  <li>400g Quinoa</li>
  <li>500ml Vegetable Broth</li>
  <li>400g Chickpeas</li>
  <li>100g dried cranberries</li>
  <li>33g finely diced flat leaf parsley</li>
  <li>64g sliced toasted almonds</li>
</ul>

<p><b>Instructions</b></p>
<ol>
  <li>Add oil, turmeric, cumin, cinnamon, salt and pepper to pot and cook (30 secs).</li>
  <li>Add quinoa and broth, bring to boil, then cover, reduce heat and cook (15 mins).</li>
  <li>Add chickpeas, cranberries, parsley and mix.</li>
  <li>Garnish with toasted almonds and parsley.</li>
</ol>

<p>Adapted from <a href="https://www.thefullhelping.com/one-pot-italian-quinoa-lentils/">thefullhelping.com</a></p>
